extendedInfo.description: Amazing live wallpaper which will allow you to enjoy the best pictures of the Death all of the time.To change the Live Wallpaper image you should do double click on the 3d cube to enter menu preferences or load the application and click in preferences menu where you can also configure the speed, transparency...To INSTALL: You should open the application and press the menu button and select the option to "Set Live Wallpaper". You can also do this from the android menu, looking for the option of Live Wallpapers and then selecting it.Tags: Skull, calavera, fire, fondo animado, death, muerte, muete
